	* device/lib/time.c (mktime): fixed bug reported by Bert Thomas
	* sdcc.spec: updated and split sdcc into 3 rpms
	* src/SDCCast.c (decorateType): &|^ don't need addCast(); addCast() is
	needed for literals of LEFT_OP and '+'
